quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  78,31,"Pellet na woodani hul…ďe Alla …ďe da…óirde."
  78,32,"Ko gese e inabeeje."
  78,33,"E (rew…ďe)∆īoolnu…ďe gi∆īiraa…ďe."
  78,34,"E ka'aseeje (sanngara) keew…óe."
  78,35,"∆Āe nanataa ndeer toon haala mehre, wonaa ko bakkondiŇčta."
  78,36,"Ko njo…ďdi ummaade e joom e dokke ke∆ī…óe."
  78,37,"joom kammu e leydi e ko woni hakkunde mu'en jurmtoo…óo mbo …ďe ngala e mum haala."
  78,38,"√Ďande jibriil ummii tawa malayka en na mba…ói sappeeji …ďe haalata si wona mbo Alla sakkitani o haala ko feewi."
  78,39,"Ko oon woni √Īalawma goongo kala paalaa…óo da…óde nanngira joomiiko ruttorde."
  78,40,"Min njeertinii on lepte …ďadii…óe √Īande aade ndaari ko juu…óe mum mba…óno ke'efeera o wi'a haaniina mi woniina lesdi."
  79,1,"Mi woo…óbdirii maleyka en poo…óooji pittaali poo…ógol ca…ótungol."
  79,2,"Mi woo…óndirii maleyka en ittat…ói pittaali e newuya."
  79,3,"Mi woo…óndirii lummbatoo…ói lummbagol."
  79,4,"Mi woo…óndarii da…óandirooji da…óndirgol."
  79,5,"Mi woo…óndirii jiilay…ói jamirooje."
  79,6,"√Īande dimmbii dimmbatndende."
  79,7,"Rewa e hendu wo…óndu ndu."
  79,8,"∆Āer…óe …óe √Īande heen no kuli."
  79,9,"Ndaar…óe mu'en no koyi."
  79,10,"He…ďe mbi'a mbela komin ruttatoo…ďe no min ngonirnoo."
  79,11,"Mbela somin ngontii ∆īi'e dappu…óe min nduttoto."
  79,12,"∆Āe mbi'a si min nduttiima sinnda de …óum wona duttal pertungal."
  79,13,"∆äuum ko ha'acaango wooto."
  79,14,"Ndeke tan …ďe ngontii wuur…ďe(ummitinaa…ď.)"
  79,15,"Taw si arii e maa…óa yewtere fii Muusaa."